{"tid":699792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［勸世文］奉勸想自殺嘅人入嚟呢個post睇一睇","createTime":"2018-06-12T21:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T11:26:41.000Z","uid":104443,"like":9,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3937a396df26554a71ac78d8b149e4f5d3de59c2","tid":699792,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T21:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/123519_a36ab141fed0d969dfca46316d7cf4da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F123519_a36ab141fed0d969dfca46316d7cf4da.png&h=fe75b758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果投着個咁豬扒嘅八婆你仲會唔會想死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而且幅圖未講仲有<br />\n1/5機會投做非洲班黑人<br />\n1/5機會投做姦國印度人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲未計中東班伊斯蘭、南美原始部落呢咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保守估計至少70%都會投咗去地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果仲要投着女人就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘅然今生「比較」有幸做到香港人，點解大家唔去珍惜，要去玩埋曬呢啲輸多贏少嘅投胎遊戲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede7945bbd32a45811015f0151fc13352933d5e0","tid":699792,"uid":17232,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T22:00:03.000Z","msg":"呢個世界無投胎"},{"pid":"2e6545b451a410e598817c8bb956460f4cec5229","tid":699792,"uid":104443,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ede7945bbd32a45811015f0151fc13352933d5e0","tid":699792,"uid":17232,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T22:00:03.000Z","msg":"呢個世界無投胎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T22:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你又知？"},{"pid":"b6fda88f2c9d0af5dff3a38825620fefd4ac